BlueberryAuth
=============

BlueberryAuth is authentication plugin (to be technically correct it's engine) inspired by such plugins
as restful-auth and clearance. It takes advantage Rails 2.2's i18n.

Testing
=======

To bootstrap testing environment you have to run following rake task:

  rake test_app:generate

And than as usual:

  rake test


